title: 820-3662 keyboard error
message: Hi , ive got an 820-3662 with a keyboard error, the bottom row of letters do not work , i have tried two other keyboards and same result, the laptop did have a liquid spill, keyboard connector looks ok, any hints as to where to start looking ??????

title: 820-3662 keyboard error
message: Check for continuity from connector to u4801

title: 820-3662 keyboard error
message: Either bad connector or bad trace from connecter to U4801.
